author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Eagle Pharmaceuticals Reports Q4 EPS Of $0.58
text:
Feb 26 (Reuters) - Eagle Pharmaceuticals Inc:
* EAGLE PHARMACEUTICALS, INC. REPORTS FOURTH QUARTER AND FULL YEAR 2017 RESULTS
* Q4 ADJUSTED NON-GAAP EARNINGS PER SHARE $1.00
* Q4 EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.58 * Q4 REVENUE $46.8 MILLION VERSUS $81.1 MILLION * Q4 EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $1.00, REVENUE VIEW $52.9 MILLION -- THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S
* 2018 RESEARCH AND DEVELOPMENT EXPENSE IS EXPECTED TO BE IN RANGE OF $46 MILLION TO $50 MILLION Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Reuters.Briefs@thomsonreuters.com)
